org.amv.trafficsoft.rest.client

Class TrafficsoftClients

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.amv.trafficsoft.rest.client.TrafficsoftClients

  • public final class TrafficsoftClients
extends java.lang.Object
    A factory class for creating client instances.

    This class exists for simpler construction of new clients for the various services to access different parts of the API.
